{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/kemu3007/portal/issues/46", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/kemu3007/portal", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/kemu3007/portal/issues/46/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/kemu3007/portal/issues/46/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/kemu3007/portal/issues/46/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/kemu3007/portal/issues/46", "id": 1244192476, "node_id": "I_kwDOG7qoq85KKN7c", "number": 46, "title": "实时绘制Mermaid.js", "user": {"login": "kemu3007", "id": 29157528, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjI5MTU3NTI4", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/29157528?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007", "html_url": "https://github.com/kemu3007", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [{"id": 3898939400, "node_id": "LA_kwDOG7qoq87oZRgI", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/kemu3007/portal/labels/article", "name": "article", "color": "C200E5", "default": false, "description": ""}, {"id": 3900074882, "node_id": "LA_kwDOG7qoq87odmuC", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/kemu3007/portal/labels/Angular", "name": "Angular", "color": "D93F0B", "default": false, "description": ""}], "state": "open", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 0, "created_at": "2022-05-22T08:54:29Z", "updated_at": "2022-05-22T11:54:51Z", "closed_at": null, "author_association": "OWNER", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "在多次使用Mermaid.js使用图表，并且绘制真实时间绘图的工具总结了和真实的时间绘图方法。\r\n\r\n＃＃ 介绍\r\n\r\n````bash\r\n$ npm我美人鱼\r\n$ npm i-save-dev @types/mermaid\r\n````````\r\n\r\n＃＃ 绘画\r\n\r\n-component.html\r\n\r\n````html\r\n<div class =“美人鱼”>\r\n序列图\r\n爱丽丝 -  >>鲍勃：你好\r\n</div>\r\n````````\r\n\r\n-component.ts\r\n\r\n``TS\r\n从“美人鱼”进口美人鱼\r\n\r\nmermaid.initialize（{startOnload：true}）\r\n````````\r\n\r\n！[image]（https：//user-bimages.githubusercontent.com/29157528/169693934-B16777538-4DED-A905-DA1A7C09.PNG）\r\n\r\n\r\n##让它再次在已经绘制的地方绘制\r\n\r\n-component.html\r\n\r\n````html\r\n<div class =“美人鱼” #Mermaid ID =“ Mermaid”>\r\n序列图\r\n爱丽丝 -  >>鲍勃：你好\r\n</div>\r\n````````\r\n\r\n-component.ts\r\n\r\n``TS\r\n从“美人鱼”进口美人鱼\r\n\r\n@ViewChild（'Mermaid'）Mermaiddiv！：ElementRef <htmldivelement>;\r\n\r\n//如果已经绘制了美人鱼，请删除它，因为授予数据处理的属性\r\nmermaiddiv.nativelement.removeattribute（'数据处理'）;\r\n//输入要绘制为InnerHTML的文本（对于Innertext的情况，有必要使用InnerHTML，因为线路断裂成为BR标签。）\r\nmermaiddiv.nativelement.innerhtml = txt;\r\n//初始化（绘图）处理\r\nMermaid.init（'#mermaid'）;\r\n````````\r\n\r\n＃＃ 在最后\r\n\r\n基于上述实现，我们创建了一个页面，该页面可实时绘制Mermaid.js并促进描述。\r\n\r\n[Mermaid Live Editor]（https://portal.kemu.site/tools/mermaid/）", "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/kemu3007/portal/issues/46/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/kemu3007/portal/issues/46/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null}